title: US Chantilly
text: Union Sportive de Chantilly is a <a href="Association%20football">football</a> club from <a href="Chantilly%2C%20Oise">Chantilly, Oise</a>, France. It was founded in 1902 and, as of the <a href="2020%E2%80%9321%20Championnat%20National%203">2020–21 season</a>, plays in the <a href="Championnat%20National%203">Championnat National 3</a>, the fifth tier of French football. The club won promotion from the sixth tier at the first attempt, after previously being relegated from the Championnat National 3 in 2019.
